cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV. 

This paper is about a neural model for coreference resolution, which is a task in natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, so cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. The model uses embeddings and attention mechanisms, which are common in neural networks, so cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is another possible category. Finally, the paper deals with text data, so cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still a possible category.
